    {
      "fieldId": "1a000003-0000-4000-a000-000000000003",
      "value": "`Field.contentFormat`, when present, is only meaningful when `valueType` is `\"string\"` or `\"text\"`. Implementations must ignore `contentFormat` on fields with any other `valueType`."
    },
